ting";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"https://community.1and1.com/?p=9669";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:638:"<p>With the 1&#38;1 Control Panel for iOS and Android, you have all important information and settings for your 1&#38;1 products right in the palm of your hand. You can quickly access important key performance indicators for your websites or change the settings for your contract, domains and websites while on the go. And if you want, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-ios-android/">1&#038;1 Control Panel for iOS and Android: Manage your Websites, Domains and Settings</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"Philipp Bellmann";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3220:"<p>With the 1&amp;1 Control Panel for iOS and Android, you have all important information and settings for your 1&amp;1 products right in the palm of your hand.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9678" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1and1-control-panel-app-overview_features-Kopie.png" alt="Control Panel for iOS and Android Features" width="7337" height="3413" />\n<p>You can quickly access important key performance indicators for your websites or change the settings for your contract, domains and websites while on the go. And if you want, you can also read interesting posts about web hosting, web design, server technology and SEO topics right in the app.</p>\n<h2>Getting to Know the Home Page</h2>\n<p>The home page gives you direct access to messages, news, statistics and domains. You can use the <strong>menu</strong> to access additional settings.</p>\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-9680" src="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1und1-control-center-en_startseite.png" alt="1und1-control-center-en_startseite" width="3834" height="2532" srcset="https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1und1-control-center-en_startseite.png 3834w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1und1-control-center-en_startseite-300x198.png 300w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1und1-control-center-en_startseite-768x507.png 768w, https://community.1and1.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1und1-control-center-en_startseite-1024x676.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 3834px) 100vw, 3834px" />\n<h2>Discovering All Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Easily manage your data and products from your smartphone.</li>\n<li>Keep track of all your invoices.</li>\n<li>Check how <u>1&amp;1 SiteAnalytics</u> is making your websites more successful.</li>\n<li>Register and manage your <u>domains</u>.</li>\n<li>Get answers to your questions in the integrated 1&amp;1 Help Center.</li>\n<li>Knowledge and good ideas make your website unique and successful. That&#8217;s why you can find interesting posts about web hosting and WordPress directly in the 1&amp;1 Control Panel.</li>\n<li>Status updates: We help you by providing background information and offering assistance with technical disruptions.</li>\n<li>Contact us easily and get personalized customer service over the phone: Create your telephone PIN directly in the app.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Downloading 1&amp;1 Control Panel</h2>\n<p>1&amp;1 Control Panel is available free of charge for iOS devices, Android smartphones and tablets with Android 4.4 or later.</p>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="promo-button" href="https://itunes.apple.com/app/1-1-control-panel/id1080444849?l=en&amp;mt=8">iOS (App Store)</a> and <a class="promo-button" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.oneandone.ciso.mobile.app.android">Android (Google Play)</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-ios-android/">1&#038;1 Control Panel for iOS and Android: Manage your Websites, Domains and Settings</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://community.1and1.com">1&amp;1 Community</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"https://community.1and1.com/1and1-control-panel-ios-android/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:63:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"Start your eCommerce Website with WordPress and WooCommerce";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:74:"https://community.1and1.com/start-ecommerce-website-wordpress-woocommerce/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:82:"https://community.1and1.com/start-ecommerce-website-wordpress-woocommerce/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s